metadata.name: RAREPUNKCARD - The Invocation Of Punks
metadata.description:
RAREPUNKCARDS are series of collectible cards available in limited quantity, more than just a unique art piece, these cards will bring different benefits to their holders.

"The Invocation Of Punks" is the first RAREPUNKCARD out before TEF launch. This card isn't part of any series and is the most limited one.
